{"tid":826462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又一單意外 樹壓巴士","createTime":"2018-09-18T09:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T10:28:16.000Z","uid":110524,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1eeda68bb703971ac5e951f4793e36d52c45fa00","tid":826462,"uid":110524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/170636_9e09fee6c2e605b381427ec08f6e6f25.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F170636_9e09fee6c2e605b381427ec08f6e6f25.png&h=729b3c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭收得皮"},{"pid":"927b402999aa41e40ded3108ae0bde80fe1708bb","tid":826462,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:07:52.000Z","msg":"邊度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a6607efd1a744c9057fabe6008e7fa20365ec5","tid":826462,"uid":110524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:08:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180918/58695766\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180918%2F58695766&d=g7k2Ncn0pY6isMlTzy50xTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=efe481ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180918%2F58695766&h=d55b5eee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180918/58695766</a>"},{"pid":"ae69e7354932f4cb7314b30c874cd54f62908ba9","tid":826462,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:09:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180918/bkn-20180918101832837-0918_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180918%2Fbkn-20180918101832837-0918_00822_001.html&d=g7k2Ncn0pY6isMlTzy50xTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=7ed0a0f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180918/bkn-20180918101832837-0918_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"59fcbe17e740c3bae885e7e9a6a9acff4876612e","tid":826462,"uid":22349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"風災過後，各區仍有大量樹木折斷阻路，更有部分椏枝造成障礙，雖然各部門已盡力清理，道路大致通暢，但即使通車後仍有行車線被大樹等雜物阻擋。今(18日)早11時許，一輛85號路線九巴，在總站開出後，駛至火炭路近山尾街時，車頂撞到塌下樹幹，導致車身受損，車長停車報案，意外中無人受傷。 <br />\n<br />\n另外2宗分別發生於將軍澳及九龍城。早上9時許，一輛93K路線九巴，駛經寶林北路時，車頭撞到路邊塌下的樹椏，部分樹椏插入擋風玻璃，車長發現即時停車報警，意外中無人受傷。早上8時許，有巿民乘搭1號線九巴沿太子道西往旺角時，稱巴士被大樹擊中，以致上層車頭擋風玻璃裂開損毀，乘客通知車長，事件中幸無人受傷，巴士其後返回車廠維修。 <br />\n<br />\n而除九巴外，一輛118號路線城巴，今晨8時許，由小西灣開出往長沙灣，期間有中途乘客上車時發現車頂被一條長約1.5米的樹枝插穿，樹枝跌在上層近車尾位置座椅上，乘客通知車長，但巴士繼續行駛，直至巴士駛至長沙灣後，車長將樹枝移走，然後將車駛回車廠維修。"},{"pid":"43303d56d789a5b08ececb08da495c72c9164abe","tid":826462,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180918/photo/bkn-20180918101832837-0918_00822_001_03p.jpg?20180918133525\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180918%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180918101832837-0918_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20180918133525&h=ecad3965&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"150005f213381822af7ae4e1fcc274f5f61daad8","tid":826462,"uid":41841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:12:58.000Z","msg":"冧樹咋？冧樓再講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c29bcad95278bc98d62aaa47882959b7f8aa35","tid":826462,"uid":25952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:13:17.000Z","msg":"好彩巴士上無乜人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de4bdc756243c3519c65daeb71cc068bb34fa5f","tid":826462,"uid":179718,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:14:54.000Z","msg":"肯定係巴士墮下後先冧樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" cl